cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to solve a benchmark dataset for single-relation factoid questions. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural networks (cs.NE) which are all relevant sub-categories.
